Obama Administration Monitoring Oil Price Drop for Retail Fraud

-- B y   J u s t i n   B l u m
-- 
2011-05-06T19:12:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/obama-administration-monitoring-oil-price-drop-for-retail-fraud.html
The Obama administration is monitoring
whether reductions in wholesale oil prices are being passed on
to consumers, Attorney General  Eric Holder  said in a memo today.  “If wholesale prices continue to decrease, fraud or
manipulation must not be allowed to prevent price decreases from
being passed on to consumers at the pump,” Holder wrote.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Justin Blum in  Washington  at 
 jblum4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
